catalog 0.1.0

This is the initial release of the {catalog} package. This release adds the full suite of functionality from the Catalog API including:

  • Caching
    • cache_table()
    • clear_cache()
    • is_cached()
    • refresh_by_path()
    • refresh_table()
    • uncache_table()
  • Columns
    • list_columns()
  • Database
    • current_database()
    • database_exists()
    • list_databases()
    • set_current_database()
  • Functions
    • function_exists()
    • get_function()
    • list_functions()
  • Partitioning
    • recover_partitions()
  • Tables
    • create_table()
    • get_table()
    • list_tables()
    • table_exists()
  • Temporary Views
    • drop_global_temp_view()
    • drop_temp_view()
